thread.title: Jacqui Edwards
thread.title_full: Official iPhone Unlock reviewed by Jacqui Edwards

author: Jacqui Edwards
title: Jacqui Edwards
text:
I feel the service you provided was very good, and appreciated the processing cycle on the web site, it enabled me to check the progress. I was dissapointed when the cycle finished and the phone was still locked. But the message update kept me up to date with situation.
My only gripe is the price - £19.99 and then another £29.99 - this is too much.
